v><div class = \"text-block\">Glucose: 0.900 g<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Hepes: 1.300 g <\/div><div class = \"text-block\">To prepare 0.5 L of HBSS\/HEPES, dissolve the reagents listed above in 450 mL of ultrapure H2O.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Adjust the pH to 7.4 with HCl or NaOH, and then add H2O to 0.5 L.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Storage: <\/span><a href=\"#\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\"> <\/span><\/a><span> Fridge 1- (Room TSO8)<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">NaCl code:<\/span><span> S9625, Sigma<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">KCl code:<\/span><span> P9541, Sigma<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">MgSO4 code:<\/span><span> 1.05886, Sigma<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">CaCl2 code:<\/span><span> 1.02382 Sigma<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Glucose code:<\/span><span> 1.08337, Sigma<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Hepes code:<\/span><span> H7006 Sigma<\/span><\/div><\/div>","materials":[],"description":null,"changed_on":1595584252}